Description:
    Installs VoiceCommand configuration files and Stimulus controller.
    This generator creates:
      - config/initializers/voice_command.rb (configuration with examples)
      - app/javascript/controllers/voice_command_audio_recorder_controller.js (Stimulus controller)

Example:
    bin/rails generate voice_command:install

    This will create:
        config/initializers/voice_command.rb
        app/javascript/controllers/voice_command_audio_recorder_controller.js

After Installation:
    1. Configure your LLM provider in the initializer
    2. Add API keys to Rails credentials
    3. Create your custom tools in app/tools/
    4. Register tools in the initializer
    5. Create a controller to handle voice command requests
    6. Add the audio recorder to your views
